385132af662b"],

Cell["\<\
This document show that the distribution of survivors when the effect of a \
dose of a risk-factor on survival is exponential and the original population \
is normal, is also normal with a shifted mean.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948778457897154*^9, 3.948778463015894*^9}, {
  3.9487785069023094`*^9, 3.948778571033579*^9}, {3.9487786119160824`*^9, 
